{
  "texts": [
    "Sometimes, to help participants get a clearer picture of content suggestions, we presented examples like content suggestions on various e-commerce websites, movie streaming websites, travel destination recommendations, etc.",
    "Such websites commonly provide users with product recommendations and some type of hint such as \"frequently watched movies\"/\"previously purchased products\".",
    "These examples helped the study participants understand what we meant by content recommendation, particularly explainable recommendations.",
    "We conducted 37 in-depth semi-structured interviews with regular Facebook users in total.",
    "On average, they spend at least two hours daily on social platforms."
  ]
}